---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Donar">
  <div
    class="flex flex-col gap-4 bg-dark-purple text-light py-16 items-center justify-center min-h-screen max-w-full w-full"
  >
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 py-4 max-w-2xl px-4 md:px-8">
      <h1
        class="text-[60px] leading-none font-bold font-redaction-20 flex flex-row flex-wrap items-center gap-6 text-shadow-sexy text-shadow-turquoise-highlight md:justify-start justify-center"
      >
        Doná a O.D.I.A.
      </h1>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
      <p class="pt-4 flex flex-col items-center *:leading-[.8]">
        <span
          class="text-8xl text-red-highlight text-bold font-redaction-20 videogame-jump text-shadow-sexy text-shadow-turquoise-highlight"
        >
          $15.000
        </span>
        <span
          class="text-2xl text-red-highlight text-bold font-redaction-20 videogame-jump text-shadow-sexy text-shadow-turquoise-highlight"
        >
          por mes
        </span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 py-4 max-w-2xl px-4 md:px-8">
      <p class="text-2xl font-merriweather">
        Si querés ayudarnos a seguir trabajando en favor de los derechos
        digitales, podes colaborar pagandonos tres birras por mes.
      </p>
      <a
        href="https://www.mercadopago.com.ar/subscriptions/checkout?preapproval_plan_id=2c938084950cbacf019515ab4b6603fc"
        class="bg-turquoise-highlight text-light font-bold text-4xl py-6 px-6 md:px-12 rounded-lg shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 text-center font-redaction-20 text-shadow-sexy text-shadow-dark hover:text-shadow-none"
      >
        Suscribite con MercadoPago
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
